pullrequest.title: qtutils 2.0.0 support and experimental PyQt5 support

content.raw:
Looking good! I find no problems in testing so far.

To actually compile shots I needed to update other labscript libraries as well, but I imagine other testers (i.e @shjohnst) will just update everything to this branch and run for a while.
